'''科波罗洛河'''（'''Coporolo'''）是[[安哥拉|安哥拉]]的一条间歇河，但有时也被认为是常年河。<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=YfERAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA8&lpg=PA8&dq=coporolo+River+intermittent&source=bl&ots=hb3YYZl9wK&sig=rvAmKYD3Ptk57X8G4F2EMXXN0Ig&hl=en&sa=X&ei=ZjvLUqSFIoP1oASitYHoCw&ved=0CEEQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=coporolo%20River%20intermittent&f=false The Earth and Its Inhabitants, Africa: South and east Africa], Elisée Reclus, D. Appleton, 1890</ref>流域面积15674km<sup>2</sup>，流入大西洋[[本格拉省|本格拉省]]海域。河口附近有城镇{{link-en|大栋贝|Dombe Grande}}。

季节性洪水是该河流长年出现的问题。2011年7月的洪水造成6700人流离失所。<ref>[http://www.opais.net/pt/opais/?id=1657&det=19469&mid= A fúria do rio Coporolo] {{Wayback|url=http://www.opais.net/pt/opais/?id=1657&det=19469&mid= |date=20140107075021 }}, O Pais, 7 - 3 -2011</ref>

